2012-08-24	v0.2.1

* Improved item name extraction, which now works correctly for linked items.
. Pop-up tooltip no longer steals focus.
. Collage no longer draws numbers for just a single item.

2012-08-16	v0.2

* New UI which now shows a list of captured items. Hovering over an item shows a pop-up tooltip of the complete item. Clicking on any item in the list removes it.
. Collage file name now uses local time instead of UTC.
